{"tid":560514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋狂奶西 Tesco 員工高潮片流出","createTime":"2018-02-14T07:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T09:10:51.000Z","uid":72009,"like":103,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd8d677ad6e121ed5dd630b8759c4922baf5fa2","tid":560514,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"英國賣場Tesco位在東英吉利(East Anglia)地區的一處分店，被兩名青少年屁孩拍到激情的一幕。有兩名疑似是Tesco員工就在賣場後方的一處辦公室，當場無恥辱性交，兩人也殊不知有人在偷窺並偷拍。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這兩名屁孩聽到辦公室傳來嘻笑聲，透過窗戶偷窺更發現，裡頭有一對男女正在上演活春宮。其中一名身穿賣場制服的女子社員，正在接受男子的口交，就在女子社員享受「品鮑」的過程中，表情一度顯露出「啊啊」的激情快感。<br />\n屁孩隨後將這段影片上傳至WhatsApp，並快速在網路鄉民間流傳，引發熱烈討論。Tesco發言人則回應，他們正在調查這起事件。台灣網友紛紛表示：「這是自家人在試年貨品質，屁孩不懂別吵。」、「過新年了！」、「產地直送鮮鮑魚！」、「辦(黏)貨。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180214/640_783f633141eeb497b5784f7cdf626bd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180214%2F640_783f633141eeb497b5784f7cdf626bd7.jpg&h=c2b2ea71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180214/640_09accf92890e113832ef46d5f2ad1ac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180214%2F640_09accf92890e113832ef46d5f2ad1ac6.jpg&h=5736adda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180214/1298328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180214%2F1298328&d=Z%2FLYlDC%2BbCiY9gyXoKvgKf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=44241f23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180214%2F1298328&h=61df1b04\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180214/1298328</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452b7c3dad245024c6ba586852613769e9f38b12","tid":560514,"uid":511,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":1